dream: Dreaming I started working with a new investor and they called an inspector to inspect the electrical work which was not complete and they were disappointed so I had to explain that part of the process.
interpretation: This dream suggests feelings of inadequacy or pressure in a new venture or project. The new investor represents a significant change or opportunity in your life, potentially related to work or a personal endeavor. However, the unfinished electrical work symbolizes incomplete or unresolved aspects of this venture, or perhaps a sense of unpreparedness or incompetence on your part. The disappointment expressed by the investor reflects a fear of not meeting expectations or facing judgment from others. Your need to explain this situation indicates a desire to justify or defend yourself in the face of potential criticism. Overall, this dream may be urging you to address any feelings of uncertainty or unpreparedness you have in order to confidently navigate new opportunities or projects.
title: Electrical Inspection Surprise: Navigating Disappointment with New Investor
